pageContext.title: The Latest From Shasta Lake
pageContext.excerpt: This time of year you can find me chasing big brown trout along the banks of lake Shasta. It’s still spring, air temperature is cool, the sun is out, the Shasta Lake has not turned yet (turning is when water temp warms for the summer).
